Hi Vibhu! I am Rathina, Co-Founder of Crio.Do, and an ex-Product Leader at Flipkart. 


Your background as System Engineer at Infosys caught my eye, and I wanted to discuss Crio and ways to accelerate one's career in software development. 

 

With a recent boom in product-based tech companies, job openings for skilled developers has grown over 100% in the last year. Developers with hands-on experience in key technologies are able to crack these jobs and rapidly grow their career. But unfortunately, gaining hands-on experience in tech skills that matter is not easy. Online video-based courses and tutorials are not effective.


This is why we launched our Fellowship Program in Software Development.


In this program, you will build multiple internship-grade projects in an actual developer environment, and learn key Full Stack or Backend skills with real work experience. Throughout your learning journey, you will receive strong support and guidance from experienced Crio mentors.
